dim and she may wax or wane.)</font> &nbsp; <font face="仿宋"> 此事古难全。(There has been nothing perfect since the olden days.)</font> &nbsp; <font face="仿宋"> 但愿人长久，(So let us wish that everyone will live long as they can!)</font> &nbsp; <font face="仿宋"> 千里共婵娟。(Though miles apart, we’ll share the beauty she displays.)</font> </div></div></div></div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="travelling"/><category term="trips"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[After three long years of the enduring pandemic, I was elated to finally make my way back to my hometown, Guangzhou. Reuniting with my family and reconnecting with old friends offered a much-needed and delightful escape from my research endeavors.]]></summary></entry></feed>